Ángela.definition: Ángela is so [wonderful]. If you know some Ángela you’re so lucky to have them [in your life], they are so loyal and funny. You can always trust an Ángela. The are [beautiful] angels that are in our world to keep us safe, so they will help you with anything. The usually are shy and the need some help too, but they will always make you laugh or simply make you happy
Ángela.example: I love [my friend] Ángela, she is so [beautiful] and funny, [you should] meet her
